Package tum.dss.thesis

This package provides interfaces for the LS Framework as well as helper functions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ItemsetHandlerInterface
    Interface for sets and subsets of items.
    LinearProgramInterface
    Interface for relaxed IP, e.g. a Gurobi Model.
    MechanismDataInterface
    Interface for the data for the mechanism.
    MechanismInterface
    Interface for an instance of a mechanism with certain parameters.
    PlayerInterface
    Interface for an individual player in the mechanism data.
    PrimalDecompositionInterface
    Interface for the primal LP of the convex decomposition model, e.g. a Gurobi model.
    SeparationOracleInterface
    Interface for the separation oracle.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MatrixHelper
    Some helper function for JScience matrices and vectors.
    Playground
    Test area only!

Package tum.dss.thesis Description

This package provides interfaces for the LS Framework as well as helper functions.
Author:
Florian Stallmann
